thread.title: Kathleen Ayala

author: Kathleen Ayala
title: Kathleen Ayala
text:
I REALIZED THAT MY PASSPORT HAD EXPIRED A COUPLE OF WEES BEFORE I WAS SCHEDULED TO GO ON VACATION. I WAS STRESSED BEYOND BELIEF. YOUR STAFF CALMED ME DOWN AND REASSURED ME THAT I WOULD RECEIVE MY PASSPORT ON TIME. I MADE AN ERROR ON THE INITIAL APPLICATION AND ONE OF YOUR MEMBERS CALLED ME AND WALKED ME THROUGH IT. I WILL DEFINITELY CONTINUE TO LET PEOPLE KNOW ABOUT YOU AND YOUR TERRIFIC SERVICE. THANK YOU AGAIN.
KATHLEEN AYALA
